Subject: RE: [T2] Aftermarket Tents

Anybody ever see a tent for the rear hatch for sale new? I think somebody on
this list pointed out a bed extender/tent for the rear of the bus that was
for sale on Ebay. According to the auction the top slid over the rear hatch
and the bottom board slid under the back cushion. It had some kind of
support that went under it.  This extended the sleeping area by about 3
feet. I thought that this may be of some interest to some people that are
looking for extra room via a small tent.

Corbett


